<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11111</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>15985</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，春天来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>15986</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19654</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>天气变暖，鲜花盛开，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19655</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23524</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鸟儿在树上飞来飞去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23525</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26455</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>师徒四人继续西行。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26456</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30173</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们准备翻过一座山。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30174</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32995</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空让大家停下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32996</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36182</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“八戒，你去看看山上的情况。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36183</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40633</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>山上可能有妖怪。我不想让师父受到伤害。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40634</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46129</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“呃。”八戒嘀咕道，“你总是让我干累活儿。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46130</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50621</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒不高兴地向山上走去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50622</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55651</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空转身对唐僧和悟净说：“我去跟着他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55652</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60584</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我要看看他是不是真的在查山。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60585</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68212</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空隐身后跟在八戒后面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68213</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73312</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒走了一会儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73313</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80798</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当他确定大家已经听不到自己的声音时，马上转过身来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80799</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85806</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你个傻瓜！”八戒大叫，“你总是让我干累活儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85807</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90501</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这次，我才不去呢！我要睡一觉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90502</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96108</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>等我回去的时候，我就撒谎说我已经查过山了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96109</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103573</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒找到了一个大木头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103574</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114716</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他躺在木头后面， 很快就睡着了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114717</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119091</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这头猪太懒了。”悟空想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119092</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121169</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要教训他一下。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121170</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125658</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空变成了一只啄木鸟，开始啄木头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125659</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129575</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哒哒哒！哒哒哒！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129576</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133992</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒翻了个身，嘴里嘟囔着什么。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133993</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140718</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空又开始啄。哒哒哒！哒哒哒！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140719</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142942</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒坐了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142943</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146058</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别再啄了，讨厌的啄木鸟！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146059</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151110</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我要睡觉！”他又睡着了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151111</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157243</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空落在八戒的头上。哒哒哒！哒哒哒！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157244</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162061</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！”八戒大叫着跳了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162062</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166040</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空飞走了。八戒挠挠头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166041</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171905</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我连打个瞌睡都不行！”他叹了口气，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171906</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174850</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我看我还是回去吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174851</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180170</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当八戒回来时，他撒了个谎。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180171</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184913</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我查了整座山。”他说，“很安全。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184914</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188976</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你看到什么妖魔鬼怪了吗？”悟空说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188977</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194775</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒摇摇头。“那啄木鸟呢？”悟空问，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194776</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197263</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你看到啄木鸟了吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197264</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203058</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒看上去很惊讶。“什么……你怎么……？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203059</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207224</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那是我啊，八戒！”悟空大叫，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207225</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211769</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你去打瞌睡了！你根本就没去查山！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211770</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214766</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒低下了头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214767</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218582</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“八戒，你觉得好意思吗？”悟净说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218583</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221192</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧皱起了眉头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221193</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224212</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“八戒，你再去查一遍吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224213</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229177</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒又走回去了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229178</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236425</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他走了一会儿，看到了一只狐狸。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236426</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240260</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我知道你是悟空！”他大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240261</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244396</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他挥舞着钉耙。狐狸跑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244397</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>248443</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一只小鸟飞过了八戒的头顶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>248444</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252174</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“离我远点儿，悟空！”八戒大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252175</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258011</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当他向那只鸟挥舞钉耙时，不小心绊倒了自己。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258012</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>262400</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“悟空！”八戒大叫，“我知道你在这里！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>262401</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>267709</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你隐身了。你还把我绊倒了！”八戒站了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>267710</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>275450</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>等他确定没有听到，也没看到悟空之后，他才继续走。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>275451</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>283181</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒每看到一个动物，都要挥舞着钉耙大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>283182</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>288714</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>路开始变得非常陡峭。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>288715</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>292919</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不一会儿，八戒走到一个洞穴前。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>292920</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>297115</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个妖怪站在洞穴门前。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>297116</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>302657</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒举起了钉耙。“你是谁？”他大声问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>302658</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>308455</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是金角大王。”妖怪说，“你是谁？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>308456</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>311535</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是猪八戒。”八戒说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>311536</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>314427</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我正护送唐僧去西天。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>314428</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>320253</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，唐僧……”妖怪嘴角扬起了笑意，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>320254</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>328187</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我听说，吃了唐僧可以长生不老。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>